casebody.data:
James Talcott, Inc., Respondent, v. Arnold Schildhaus, Appellant.

(Republished.)

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondent. No opinion. The date for the bill of particulars to be served shall be fixed in the order. Settle order on notice. Present — Peek, P. J., Dore, Cohn, Bastow and Botein, JJ. [See ante, p. 1029.]
